WEBVTT

00:00:00.602 --> 00:00:01.726
Moshkovitsh.

00:00:02.543 --> 00:00:03.448
UNK

00:00:04.872 --> 00:00:11.160
in Oyshvits hob ikh gehat a khavertorin, a undz ze'mir geven shkheynes meydlekh geven.

00:00:11.318 --> 00:00:17.809
zi iz elter geven fun mir mit a yor. zi iz geven hoykh, un ikh bin geven niderik un dar.

00:00:19.148 --> 00:00:23.057
zi hot men shtendik oysgekloybn in krematoryum arayn.

00:00:24.025 --> 00:00:27.006
zi iz oykh koydem gekumen mit mir oyf arbet,

00:00:27.214 --> 00:00:35.544
in Oyshvits hot zi Mengele oysgekloybn. un nokh dem yedes mol, vifl mol Mengele hot ibergekloybn, hot er zi alts aroysgevorfn.

00:00:36.715 --> 00:00:40.944
un ze'mir geven fir sh- meydlekh, fir shkheynim,

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:46.124
ale fir meydlekh, zey zenen geven ale elter, ikh bin geven di yingste.

00:00:47.042 --> 00:00:52.470
zey hobn alts geklert vos m'ken ton, mayn khavertorin Goldi,

00:00:52.527 --> 00:00:57.498
m'zol zi kenen rateven fun Mengele's hent.

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:05.649
ze'mir gegan dort hot men undz geshikt eyn mol in der vokh hot men undz gefirt bodn. dort hot undz Mengele oyfbakukt.

00:01:05.689 --> 00:01:07.843
dos heyst geheysn di zone.

00:01:09.098 --> 00:01:14.132
dort, fun dort mikh hot men alts oysgekloybn oyf arbet.

00:01:14.132 --> 00:01:21.123
un zi hot alts avekgevorfn. zi hot men alts geleygt, az m'hot alts gefunen oyf ir epes a shprenkele.

00:01:21.923 --> 00:01:26.776
bin ikh antlofn fun dort, m'hot mir gekent shisn.

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:34.741
mikh hot men avek gevolt aveknemen in der arbet. ikh hob nisht gevolt geyn, vayl ale mayne mentshn, mayne bakonte, zenen geblibn.

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:38.049
mikh hot men koydem gevolt oyf Daytshland firn.

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:47.331
bin ikh antlofn durkh ir. zi ho- ho'mir gefunen un zi iz vayter geven mit undz.

00:01:48.265 --> 00:01:54.452
nokh dem vayter hot men undz vayter ongehoybn tsu kloybn, zi hot men vayter aroysgevorfn.

00:01:54.947 --> 00:01:59.379
undz ze'mir shoyn geven oder in transport tsu geyn

00:01:59.689 --> 00:02:04.965
oyf Daytshland. undz hot men shoyn nisht aroysgelozt, undz ho'mir shoyn geheysn blok SPERRE.

00:02:06.270 --> 00:02:16.591
vi m'hot zey aroys- iz vi ze- ze'mir gekumen ahin in der zone, hot zi Mengele vayter aroysgevorfn.

00:02:17.273 --> 00:02:21.975
un fun dort iz geven, m'hot zi avekgefirt in a revir.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:27.175
a revir UNK. dos iz a neyn.

00:02:24.664 --> 00:02:25.923
UNK

00:02:27.175 --> 00:02:30.024
dos iz a UNK.

00:02:31.532 --> 00:02:35.728
un undz ho'mir nisht gevust vu dos iz, un undz hot men nisht aroysgelozt.

00:02:37.152 --> 00:02:43.507
di meydlekh hobn gezogt m'darf Go- Goldi zol zayn mit undz, vayl oyb nisht, Goldi geyt in krematoryum arayn.

00:02:45.167 --> 00:02:51.202
iz tsugegan- iz es, bin ikh gegangen UNK m'hot undz nisht aroysgelozt, vayl s'geven blok SPERRE.

00:02:51.664 --> 00:02:56.079
hobn zey gezogt di meydlekh az zol ikh veynen az s'tut mikh vey di boykh.

00:02:56.237 --> 00:02:58.931
az m'zol mikh lozn UNK tualet.

00:02:59.342 --> 00:03:04.803
ikh hob ongehoybn tsu veynen s'tut mikh vey der boykh, un ikh bin gelofn zukhn Goldin.

00:03:04.928 --> 00:03:10.662
dos iz geven in lager dort. nor dort hot men s'geven ful bra- barakn,

00:03:10.662 --> 00:03:16.633
oder m'hot nisht getort geyn in ergets fun eyn barak in andern arayn. un ikh hob zi gefunen.

00:03:18.563 --> 00:03:26.184
nor un ikh hob shoyn gekent tun az zi zol aroyskumen fun dort, vayl dort iz geven a kalitke.

00:03:26.950 --> 00:03:29.306
nor di kalitke hot men gekent oyfmakhn.

00:03:30.190 --> 00:03:36.562
un undz hot men shoyn oyfgenumen loyt dem nomen un undz ze'mir shoyn gedarft avekforn.

00:03:38.357 --> 00:03:44.409
un do hot men do iz shoyn nisht do keyn shum min, azoy vi ikh hob zi geho- getrofn,

00:03:44.668 --> 00:03:47.964
ze'm- m'hot undz aroysgelozt oyfn hoyf makhn apel,

00:03:47.964 --> 00:03:53.758
vu s'geven poylishe meydlekh, di shrayberins, vos zey hobn undz oyfgenumen, zey zenen shoyn geven fir yor in lager.

00:03:54.625 --> 00:03:58.820
hobn zey gezogt, yo ho'mir undz gezogt az mir viln mir baytn.

00:03:58.877 --> 00:04:03.278
az zi zol kumen tsun undz un an andere zol geyn ahin.

00:04:03.278 --> 00:04:10.560
hot zi gezogt, vayl undz ho'mir getrofn a froy, undz ho'mir in hoyf ongehoybn tsu shrayen ver s'vil geyn ahin in revir arayn.

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:13.350
hot zikh ongerufn eyn froy az zi vil geyn.

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:20.001
un zi iz avek ahin in revir, UNK, hot zi gezogt, di shrayberin, az zi ken gornisht tun.

00:04:20.001 --> 00:04:24.605
vayl dos iz shoyn oyfgenumen yedn loyt dem nomen un zi ken gornisht tun.

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:28.639
un hot zi gezogt far der froy, "nokh vos geystu ahin?

00:04:28.662 --> 00:04:31.153
du veyst vos dort iz?" zogt zi, yo.

00:04:31.378 --> 00:04:37.160
zogt zi, far vos vilstu geyn ahin? zogt zi, far dort iz mayn mame un ikh vil shtarbn in eynem mit mayn mame.

00:04:39.917 --> 00:04:46.155
iz di ze'mir gegangen un hobn zi avekgefirt un Goldin aroysgenumen.

00:04:46.617 --> 00:04:51.504
Goldi iz vayter gegangen mit undz in transport, oder do heybt zikh on vayter a Mengele.

00:04:52.303 --> 00:04:56.431
un di vagonen zenen shoyn geshtanen un do iz shoyn nisht geven keyn shum min hilf.

00:04:58.615 --> 00:05:02.473
hobn di meydlekh gezogt az ikh zol geyn foroys, vayl ikh vel durkhgeyn.

00:05:03.576 --> 00:05:06.214
un zey ebn blaybn fun hintn mit Goldin.

00:05:06.214 --> 00:05:08.615
ober dos iz geven azoy vi a ⟨PE⟩ gemakht.

00:05:08.757 --> 00:05:12.810
zey hobn mikh gekent fun hintn zen, vi azoy ikh bin arayn do un Mengele hot mikh bakukt,

00:05:12.810 --> 00:05:16.310
m'hot gedarft arayngeyn in der zone bodn zikh un fun dort aroysgeyn

00:05:16.310 --> 00:05:20.472
iz shoyn geven an ander plats, nor vi azoy zey zenen ges- -shtanen fun hintn,

00:05:20.472 --> 00:05:25.170
hobn zey mikh gezen ale. vi azoy ikh, zey hobn gekukt vi azoy ikh gey aroys.

00:05:25.547 --> 00:05:27.532
ikh bin aroysgegangen shnel fun dort,

00:05:27.775 --> 00:05:31.644
ikh hob gekukt az s'zol zayn shoyn a tsen fuftsn mentshn,

00:05:31.644 --> 00:05:37.606
un ikh hob ge- tsiterdike hent gehaltn dos vaser in di hent, un a shray gegebn, "Goldi, loyf!"

00:05:38.068 --> 00:05:43.305
un Goldi iz gelofn. zi hot zikh geshtelt geven tsu shmirn un, undz ze'mir ale naket geven.

00:05:43.305 --> 00:05:47.785
ikh hob ir afile gegebn a shtroy vaser, vifl ikh hob gehat in di hent,

00:05:47.785 --> 00:05:51.953
un UNK di daytshn hobn in akht genumen, az emetser iz gelofn.

00:05:51.953 --> 00:05:56.304
nor az m'hot ibergetseylt, zey hobn nisht farshtanen vos dos iz.

00:05:56.631 --> 00:06:02.092
un azoy ze'mir arayn, avekgeforn ale oyf Daytshland. SO mer keyn Mengele iz shoyn nisht geven.

00:06:03.668 --> 00:06:07.155
UNK

00:06:05.710 --> 00:06:07.644
DA UNK

00:06:08.562 --> 00:06:10.356
UNK

00:06:10.356 --> 00:06:11.593
UNK

00:06:12.662 --> 00:06:15.997
ze'mir aheymgekumen funem konts-lager, zi iz alts geven krank.

00:06:16.375 --> 00:06:21.397
un ir foter iz aheymgekumen funem konts-lager. azoy vi ikh hob keynem nisht gehat,

00:06:22.652 --> 00:06:26.454
undz ze'mir geven shkheynim, hot ir tate gezogt,

00:06:26.454 --> 00:06:31.792
az deys vos er vet esn vel ikh oys esn, un mikh lot er nisht in ergets vayl ikh hob nisht vu tsu geyn.

00:06:33.148 --> 00:06:36.213
ikh bin dokh dokh geven nor a kind un ikh hob keynem nisht.

00:06:36.523 --> 00:06:39.014
nu di momentn iz geven shtark shvere.

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:41.344
ikh hob a sakh geveynt.

00:06:44.235 --> 00:06:48.279
UNK

00:06:47.897 --> 00:06:48.991
UNK

00:06:48.991 --> 00:06:50.928
UNK

00:06:50.496 --> 00:06:57.847
UNK

00:06:52.791 --> 00:06:54.641
UNK

00:06:55.440 --> 00:06:58.100
UNK

00:07:00.013 --> 00:07:02.268
UNK

00:07:00.098 --> 00:07:01.914
UNK yidish?

00:07:03.996 --> 00:07:08.783
ven ze'mir ongekumen oyf Oyshvits, hot men gezogt di mener ekster.

00:07:09.885 --> 00:07:18.097
der di mener zenen avek ekster, un ikh mit der mame mit di kinder mit di fir briderlekh ze'mir geven in eynem.

00:07:18.964 --> 00:07:27.261
s'hot nisht gedoyert a tsen minut hot der tate gezen vu undz ze'mir, hot er mir gebrengt a shtikl broyt,

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:32.627
un a keml, az ikh zol zikh hobn mit vos tsu kemen vayl ales hot men undz tsugenumen. er hot dos gefunen oyf der erd dort.

00:07:33.308 --> 00:07:38.989
un m'ot ongehoybn, di daytshn hobn ongehoybn tsu shrayen, iz er tsurik antlofn. SO deys hob ikh im gezen, nisht mer.

00:07:39.552 --> 00:07:44.895
un mentshn hobn gezogt az er hot oysgehaltn dem lager, bakonte,

00:07:44.901 --> 00:07:50.109
nokh dem lager iz er geshtorbn, ergets in Daytshland. vu, veys ikh nisht.

00:07:54.317 --> 00:07:56.808
UNK

00:07:56.815 --> 00:07:58.828
UNK

00:07:58.570 --> 00:07:59.711
UNK

00:07:58.828 --> 00:08:02.119
UNK

00:08:02.119 --> 00:08:05.078
UNK

00:08:02.468 --> 00:08:03.491
UNK

00:08:05.083 --> 00:08:09.127
UNK

00:08:08.509 --> 00:08:10.393
UNK BETACH.

00:08:11.260 --> 00:08:14.277
iz fun der Royter Kreyts ven hot undz ibergenumen,

00:08:14.277 --> 00:08:19.120
un gekumen groyse mashinen, last-oytos, un hobn gebrengt peklekh.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:22.391
zet es oys, zey zenen shoyn gevoyer gevorn az dort iz yidn.

00:08:23.848 --> 00:08:29.967
un zey hobn undz gebrengt di peklekh. undz ho'mir shoyn nisht gekent geyn in an ergets, vayl der front iz shoyn gegangen.

00:08:30.244 --> 00:08:31.911
nisht aher nisht ahin.

00:08:31.911 --> 00:08:34.189
nor fornt mit undz iz geven

00:08:34.189 --> 00:08:41.117
ale daytsher, di ofitsirn, di soldatn, velkhe zenen geven mit undz in eynem in Gaystlingen un in Minkhn Alekh,

00:08:41.117 --> 00:08:48.041
iz dey ale gegangen mit undz. nor zey hobn gehat a gute kuper, a sheynem ⟨tsugnish⟩ geven un undz ho'mir gehat proste vagonen.

00:08:48.823 --> 00:08:53.503
un ven undz ho'm- m'hot shoyn gezen az der front nentert zi

00:08:53.503 --> 00:09:00.278
un zey hobn shoyn nisht gekent geyn in ergets nisht, vayl shoyn di amerikaner zenen shoyn ongekumen. iz ongekumen di tanken,

00:09:00.278 --> 00:09:06.165
ho'mir undz gezen az di daytshn velkhe zenen geven mit undz in di vagonen az zey nemen zikh epes tsu pakn zikh.

00:09:06.559 --> 00:09:10.091
ober keyner hot nisht gevust vos dos iz. zey hobn zikh tsamgepakt,

00:09:10.091 --> 00:09:12.999
di tsvey soldatn vos zenen gezesn in vagon,

00:09:13.073 --> 00:09:17.522
un zenen avek un zey hobn undz tsugeshpart fun droysn undz zol'mir nisht kenen aroysgeyn.

00:09:18.777 --> 00:09:24.626
un di mener hobn gezen az di tanken geyen. vayl zey zenen dokh geven in ofene vagonen.

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:28.878
hobn zey gezen di tanken. un v- m'hot gevolt shisn.

00:09:28.911 --> 00:09:34.884
zenen zey gegangen, ver vos hot ge- vi azoy er hot gekent, di shtikl hemd hobn zey tserisn, un zey hobn aroysgeleygt vayse fonen,

00:09:34.948 --> 00:09:39.290
un azoy ze'mir undz gevo- hot men oyfgehert tsu shisn. az s'iz yidn.

00:09:40.933 --> 00:09:51.521
un un u- undz ale meydlekh ho'mir gemeynt az m'harget undz. undz ze'mir geven oyf dem gegreyt, vayl ale m'hot bakumen a zekl az m'vet undz aro- m'firt undz oyf di Tirol berg un m'vet undz aropvarfn.

00:09:51.521 --> 00:09:55.305
vi azoy, vos, veyst men nisht. az yedn vet men araynleygn in a zak arayn.

00:09:56.610 --> 00:10:02.291
ven m'hot ongehoybn tsu shisn ho'mir zikh ale meydlekh tsamgenumen tsuzamen, in vagon,

00:10:02.398 --> 00:10:10.661
un ho'mir gezogt in eynem vil'mir shtarbn. s-UNK vos a khilek in tsi ekster tsi vi azoy, ale in eynem.

00:10:11.140 --> 00:10:14.199
un oyf dem hobn oyfgemakht di amerikaner di tir.

00:10:14.199 --> 00:10:19.959
un zey hobn gezogt, ir zent fray. undz ho'mir nisht geshtelt zikh nisht gekent forshteln az ze'mir bafrayt gevorn.

00:10:20.556 --> 00:10:23.132
nokh dem s'shoyn oyfgemakht ale vagonen,

00:10:23.205 --> 00:10:27.384
m'hot shoyn gekhapt di ale daytshn velkhe zenen antlofn, m'hot zey shoyn avekgefirt,

00:10:27.812 --> 00:10:31.468
un undz ho'mir shoyn ongehoybn tsu geyn zukhn a shtikl broyt.

00:10:31.879 --> 00:10:36.719
iz geven a vagonen, epes eyn vagon iz geven vos iz geven esnvarg.

00:10:36.719 --> 00:10:40.597
i far undz i far di daytshn. nu, zey hobn bakumen besers.

00:10:40.722 --> 00:10:44.681
iz vifl mener zey hobn gekent nebekh, velkhe zey hobn nokh gehat koyekh,

00:10:45.683 --> 00:10:51.414
zenen zey gegangen hobn oyfgerisn di vagonen un yeder hot gekh- gerisn zikh gekhapt a bisl esn.

00:10:54.458 --> 00:10:59.146
un un nokh dem ze'mir hot men undz arayngefirt in dorf. dos iz geven i der Ifldorf,

00:10:59.146 --> 00:11:01.927
i der Sh- i Lishtaltaykh. ikh gedenk nisht.

00:11:02.170 --> 00:11:04.951
un dort tsu dray tog hobn undz di amerikaner,

00:11:04.951 --> 00:11:08.727
in di hayzer ze'mir geven. mer keyn daytsh iz shoyn dort nisht geven.

00:11:09.443 --> 00:11:13.671
un undz ho'mir gedarft nor esn. nor esn ho'mir gekukt,

00:11:13.671 --> 00:11:19.135
ze'mir arayn in di hayzer zukhn esn. vu nor geblibn esn hot men genumen. a bisl ontun zikh,

00:11:19.956 --> 00:11:21.688
m'iz dokh geven naket POCHTI.

00:11:23.331 --> 00:11:28.590
un nokh dem hot men undz avekgenumen. dray tog hot men gelozt m'zol UNK tun vos m'vil,

00:11:28.849 --> 00:11:32.572
un m'hot men tsamgenumen un m'hot undz avekgefirt oyf Landsberg.

00:11:33.642 --> 00:11:37.466
iz geven a groyser kanzarm, dort iz geven a daytsher kazarm.

00:11:38.248 --> 00:11:44.114
un di amerikaner, shtark a sakh mentshn geven, nokh fremde oykhet, rusishe, farshidene mentshn iz geven dort.

00:11:44.256 --> 00:11:48.755
un dort azoy vi ze'mir geven shtark opgehungert un opgemogerte,

00:11:49.015 --> 00:11:51.658
hot men undz shoyn nisht gegebn oyf a mol esn,

00:11:51.850 --> 00:11:57.159
az m'zol zikh nisht fardarbn, m'zol nisht oysshtarbn, vayl zeyer a sakh mentshn zenen geshtorbn.

00:11:57.857 --> 00:12:06.221
hot men undz gegebn gemoln fleysh mit kashe. yedn tog hot men undz gekokht gemoln fleysh un yede vokh hot men undz gevoygn,

00:12:06.345 --> 00:12:08.342
tsi mir nem'mir on a bisl.

00:12:08.342 --> 00:12:11.554
un m'hot shtark opgehit az m'zol nisht epes a khap ton.

00:12:13.213 --> 00:12:17.510
nokh dem, un zey hobn undz gefirt shoyn oyf Tshekhoslovakay.

00:12:18.445 --> 00:12:21.746
ze'mir ongekumen di ershte shtot oyf Belzn.

00:12:22.748 --> 00:12:26.522
oykhet in a restorant, m'hot undz gegebn esn.

00:12:27.405 --> 00:12:30.031
nor fun dort ze'mir durkhgeforn oyf Prag,

00:12:30.561 --> 00:12:35.029
Prag hot men undz oykhet iberol, der Dzhoynt hot shoyn gevart undz iberol.

00:12:35.029 --> 00:12:38.700
iberol hot men gegebn esn, iberol hot men gegebn a por heler.

00:12:38.700 --> 00:12:41.203
un fun dort ze'mir ongekumen oyf Bratislava.

00:12:42.205 --> 00:12:48.459
Bratislava ze'mir geven epes tsvey vokhn oykhet, in a shul, in a hotel hot men oysgeleydikt.

00:12:48.718 --> 00:12:53.178
oykh gegebn a bisl un a bisele esn. iberol hot men undz gegebn esn.

00:12:53.178 --> 00:12:58.618
un fun dortn ze'mir avekgegangen, hot men undz avekgefirt, zeyer shver geven tsu forn mit di tseger,

00:12:59.130 --> 00:13:02.229
oyf der oyf der shteyger fun der oyvn.

00:13:02.860 --> 00:13:04.862
ze'mir ongekumen oyf Budapest.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:12.051
in Budapest ze'mir vayter geven a tsvey dray vokhn, un dort iz shoyn geven fray. ver vemen hot gevolt hot er shoyn gekent geyn.

00:13:13.035 --> 00:13:19.037
un ikh hob alts gevart az der tate vet kumen funem lager oykh aheym.

00:13:19.498 --> 00:13:23.030
un gekumen rakhover mentshn vos zey hobn gekent mayn tatn,

00:13:23.030 --> 00:13:27.778
hobn zey gezogt, s'nishto vos tsu vartn, nokhn bafrayenishn iz er ge- iz er geshtorbn.

00:13:30.012 --> 00:13:33.111
un nokh dem hot zikh ongehoybn shver dos lebn aleyn.

00:13:34.213 --> 00:13:36.384
UNK

00:13:35.918 --> 00:13:37.093
WRACHOWA.

